Direct Known Subclasses:
AntSystemRank
public abstract class ElitistAntSystem
extends AntSystem

This class belong to the core classes of the Ant Framework. Implements the Elitits Ant System algorithm. It is essentially the same as Ant System, but the arcs of the best-so-far tour are reinforced on each iteration using the daemonActions() function. Empirical results shows that this behaves better that Ant System.

Author:
Enrique Areyan, enrique3 at gmail.com
